  </info>
  <refnamediv>
    <refname>btkSetPointNumber</refname>
    <refpurpose>Set the number of points</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>btkSetPointNumber(h, pn)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>h</term>
        <listitem><para>The handle used to represent an acquisition.</para></listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>pn</term>
        <listitem><para>The new number of points.</para></listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>Resize the number of points.</para>
    <para>The acquisition is represented by the handle <literal>h</literal>. This handle is obtained  by the use of a btk* function.</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Examples</title>
    <programlisting role="example">btkSetPointNumber(h, 10)</programlisting>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>See Also</title>
